metadata.description:
All their lives Aries can persistently chase after the meaning of life, but they never get it. More precisely, in fact they find it very quickly, they just do not notice it. Thus, having achieved one goal, they will immediately set themselves the next. The most important thing for Aries is work, activity, process, the feeling of their indispensability. If all this is taken away from them, they will suffer. Therefore, in order to be happy, Aries simply need constant activity, movement.

Resolution 2048*2048 pixels
